  "description": [
    "Friday 3 November 1961 NWC Officers Nominated For Promotion Twentynine staff and student officers of the Naval War College have been nominated by selection boards in Washington D C for promotion to the ranks of Cap tain and Commander Two Supply Corps officers stu dents in the Naval Warfare Course selected for promotion to Captain are CDRs George E Hauge and John M Lewis Jr Other Supply Corps officers nom inated for promotion to Com mander are LCDRs Arthur W Holfleld Jr Robert G Henrich Robert W LaPlante Carlton B Smith and Robert S Sylvest Staff officers selected for pro motion to Commander are LCDRs Richard J Mc\u00dfostie and Robert G Thomson Jr Other NWC officers selected for promotion to Commander all stu dents in the Command and Staff Course are LCDRs Carl J Boyd Robert G Bowerman Richard G Colquhon Walter W Doescher Jr James C Ferguson Thomas A Graham Delbert D Grantham Donald R Jex John W Johnston John D Langford Robert C May John W Miller Robert C Pen iston Mernl C Pinkpank Charles F Richelieu Henry L Smith John C Smith George F Tolson Jr Jack R Voorhees and Walter T Zebrowski NROTC Students Musi Serve"
